name: KINDNESS LILY FLORanimal by Cat Brown/Treasvre Trove
description:
This extremely beautiful KINDNESS LILY Floranimal has appeared from the Kingdom of KIKI on the far Southern Blockchain to raise support and awareness for the Rogers and Rosewater Organization. Special thanks to TRASHEMPRESS for connecting and raising awareness.

Floranimals are hybrid RL plant matter and digital meta that live in the Kingdom of KIKI.
